    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Thy brid-al cham-ber, O my Sav---iour,_______ do I be-hold all a-dorned now, and I have not a gar---ment_______ that I may en-ter there-in. Il-lu-mine the gar--ment of__ my soul, O Light-be-stow-er,__ and save me.\n\nO Light-be-stow-er and save___ me.____"
